tora-san 's love ( 男はつらいよ &lt;unk&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : torajirō shinjitsu ) is a 1982 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and sayuri yoshinaga as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san 's lovesick is the &lt;unk&gt; entry in the popular , long-running otoko wa tsurai yo series .